content:
You are here: SALESFORCE HELP

Gather and Verify Info About Your Insurance Org

Confirm which version of packages you're using.

In Setup, find and select Installed Packages, then note the Version Number of the following packages:

Vlocity Insurance
Vlocity Installation Assistant INS
vlocity_ins_unmanaged

Answer essential questions about your org.
What type of org do you have?
Dev sandbox (Dev, early QA)
Partial sandbox (QA org)
Full sandbox (UAT, possibly QA org)
Production

Is Vlocity Contract Lifecycle Management in use?

Find and select Vlocity Templates,
Check the Last Modified By ID column value for each template.

Verify that Vlocity Support Processes are active.
Verify that the Allow Activities option is selected on the Activity Template object.
Verify that the Party.EnablePartyModel custom setting exists in your org.
title: Preparing for Salesforce Insurance Upgrade
